movie_name: Israel and Gaza: Into the Abyss
short_description: Israelis and Palestinians recount the attack of October 7, 2023, perpetrated by Hamas, and the incessant bombardments that have hit Gaza ever since.Raw testimonies, documented by amateur videos of rare violence.
